maxSeries.description: Maximum number of sets performed during the exercise

maxWeight.description: Maximum weight lifted during the exercise (in kilograms)

effortLevel.description: Indicates the perceived level of effort during the workout.

maxRepeat.description: Maximum number of repetitions achieved in a single set

averageRestTime.description: Average rest time between sets (in seconds)

notes.description: Optional notes or observations about the exercise session
notes.example: Struggled on the last set, reduce weight next time.

sessionId.description: ID of the related workout session (optional)

exerciseId.description: ID of the exercise being logged

userId.description: ID of the user who performed the exercise

createdAt.description: Date and time when the log was created
